::Striker/Mosquitor/Zenyak/Prowl::

Striker's gun drops from his hand as Hell Beast steps on it. Zenyak grins, 
pointing his gun at Striker's head. "Goodbye, fool..." Zenyak says.

Zenyak's head jerks up as a scream pierces the air. Mosquitor, chest plate 
smoking, comes falling out of the sky and crashes into Zenyak, sending him 
hurling at Hell Beast. Prowl flies down from the sky.

"Come on, bug, put a little more effort into it," Prowl says, firing at 
Mosquitor, Zenyak, and Hell Beast.

Striker jumps up and fires at them from his shoulder blasters while diving 
for his own gun.

Mosquitor stands up, stumbling back from the shots. He jumps at Prowl, fists 
swinging.
